#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to_parquet.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.to\\_parquet"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:1 of
msgid ""
"Write a DataFrame to the binary parquet format, each chunk will be "
"written to a Parquet file."
msgstr ""
"将 DataFrame 写入二进制 parquet 格式，每个 chunk 将被写入一个 Parquet "
"文件。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:4 of
msgid ""
"If path is a string with wildcard e.g. '/to/path/out-*.parquet', "
"`to_parquet` will try to write multiple files, for instance, chunk (0, 0)"
" will write data into '/to/path/out-0.parquet'. If path is a string "
"without wildcard and partition_cols is None, all data will be written "
"into a single file. If path is a string without wildcard or "
"partition_cols is not None, we will treat it as a directory."
msgstr ""
"如果 path 是带有通配符的字符串，例如 '/to/path/out-*.parquet'，`to_"
"parquet` 会尝试写入多个文件，例如 chunk (0, 0) 会将数据写入 '/to/path/out"
"-0.parquet'。如果 path 是不带通配符的字符串且 partition_cols 为 None，"
"所有数据将被写入单个文件。如果 path 是不带通配符的字符串或 partition_cols"
" 不为 None，我们将把它视为一个目录。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:12 of
msgid ""
"Parquet library to use. The default behavior is to try 'pyarrow', falling"
" back to 'fastparquet' if 'pyarrow' is unavailable."
msgstr ""
"使用的 Parquet 库。默认行为是尝试使用 'pyarrow'，如果 'pyarrow' 不可用则"
"回退到 'fastparquet'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:15 of
msgid "Name of the compression to use. Use ``None`` for no compression."
msgstr "要使用的压缩名称。使用 ``None`` 表示不压缩。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:17 of
msgid ""
"If ``True``, include the dataframe's index(es) in the file output. If "
"``False``, they will not be written to the file. If ``None``, similar to "
"``True`` the dataframe's index(es) will be saved. However, instead of "
"being saved as values, the RangeIndex will be stored as a range in the "
"metadata so it doesn't require much space and is faster. Other indexes "
"will be included as columns in the file output."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ``True``，则在文件输出中包含 dataframe 的索引。如果为 ``False``，"
"则不会将索引写入文件。如果为 ``None``，类似于 ``True``，dataframe 的索引"
"会被保存。但是，RangeIndex 不会作为值保存，而是作为元数据中的范围存储，"
"因此不占用太多空间且速度更快。其他索引将作为列包含在文件输出中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:25 of
msgid ""
"Column names by which to partition the dataset. Columns are partitioned "
"in the order they are given. Must be None if path is not a string."
msgstr ""
"用于对数据集进行分区的列名。列按给定顺序进行分区。如果 path 不是字符串，"
"则必须为 None。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datastore.to_parquet.to_parquet:29 of
msgid "Additional arguments passed to the parquet library."
msgstr "传递给 parquet 库的附加参数。"

